   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Morgan_196285_1820_11_26_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Hotel-Vauban_FR">Hotel Vauban</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  366 Rue S<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. Honoré<lb/>
                  <date when="1820-11-26">Nov.26,1820.</date>
               </dateline>
               <lb/>
            </opener>
            <p>You asked me to send a<lb/>
               letter for you to M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. <persName ref="./Personography.xml#StewD1">Dugald<lb/>
               Stewart</persName> and I think you<lb/>
               said a copy of your <choice>
                  <orig>trans<lb/>
               -lation</orig>
                  <reg>translation</reg>
               </choice>of his play, you<lb/>
               must send <add>or bring</add> it to me on<lb/>
               one of three succeeding<lb/>
               days - namely, Monday<lb/>
               Tuesday &amp; Wednesday for<lb/>
               <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Morgan_196285_1820_11_26_page02.jpg"/>
               
               I go on Thursday - Now<lb/>
               I am never at home past<lb/>
               eleven o'clock -<lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName>
               <lb/>
               Sunday<lb/>
               <pb n="3" facs="Edgeworth_Morgan_196285_1820_11_26_page03.jpg"/>
               <pb n="4" facs="Edgeworth_Morgan_196285_1820_11_26_page04.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>Monsieur</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Mons<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BuchJ1">Buchon</persName>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>4 Rue Hautefeuille</addrLine>
               </address>
               <note>MA 14215</note>
               <lb/>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
